'''4A Games'''是一家坐落在[[乌克兰|乌克兰]][[基辅|基辅]]的[[电脑游戏|电脑游戏]]开发工作室<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.4a-games.com/|title=4A Games|work=Last FM|accessdate=4 April 2013|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305092517/http://www.4a-games.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，知名作品為《[[地铁2033_(游戏)|地铁2033]]》和《[[地铁：最后的曙光|地铁：最后的曙光]]》<ref name="announcement">{{cite web|url=http://ps3.ign.com/articles/726/726243p1.html|title=First Look: Metro 2033|date=2006-08-17|accessdate=2013-11-06|archive-date=2012-04-28|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67GJCxW58?url=http://ps3.ign.com/articles/726/726243p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

4A Games由一群年轻专业人士组成，他们联合起来创立了这一全新的娱乐产业机构。员工在程序编写和电脑游戏方面拥有多年经验，尤其是在演艺界，公共事务方面。2020年8月，瑞典娱乐集团{{le|Embracer Group|Embracer Group}}宣布收购了4A Games在内的7家公司，4A Games将作为Embracer Group旗下游戏公司{{le|佩剑互动|Saber Interactive}}的子公司。<ref>[https://www.ign.com/articles/4a-games-embracer-metro-sequel-multiplayer-new-game Metro Developer Acquired By Embracer Group, Working on Metro and 'New AAA IP'] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/4a-games-embracer-metro-sequel-multiplayer-new-game |date=20201130111924 }}.IGN.2020-08-13.[2020-08-14].</ref>

